rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0001
rows.name: So, where are we supposed to go now...

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Going back isn't going to help
us, so we should probably just
keep moving forward, right?

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Yeah, I guess so... We don't have
any other option but to go forward.

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0004
rows.name:
Looks like our only way is
over that collapsed building.

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0005
rows.name:
We've got him with us, but he's not at
full strength, and we're down quite a
few fighters compared to normal...

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0006
rows.name:
We should move forward
carefully and stay alert.
